### TaksiWebApi All Endpoints Testing
@baseUrl = https://localhost:5001

# ===========================================
# USERS ENDPOINTS
# ===========================================

### Get all users
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users

### Get user by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/1

### Get user by phone
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/phone/+1234567890

### Get user by email
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/email/user@example.com

### Get active users
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/active

### Get users paginated
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/paginated?pageNumber=1&pageSize=5

### Get users count
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/count

### Search users
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/search?searchTerm=John

